Info about project 
--------------------------------------------------------------------

Database: sqlite

--------------------------------------------------------------------

install libraries:
    http://code.google.com/p/python-twitter/
    https://github.com/simplegeo/python-oauth2
    tweepy
   
python manage.py syncdb   - to create database with tables

--------------------------------------------------------------------

Put your configuration file (twitt.cnf) into the root directory. 

--------------------------------------------------------------------

python manage.py runserver
python filldb.py   - fill database (default category) (only the first time)
python updatedb.py  - update database (default category) 

!!!  it - default category  !!!

'http://127.0.0.1:8000' - home page
'http://127.0.0.1:8000/categories' - categories page
'http://127.0.0.1:8000/{category}'  - category's page

'http://127.0.0.1:8000/it'  - IT category page

--------------------------------------------------------------------

